#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:6
msgid ""
"A *Camera* is an object that provides a means of rendering images from Blender. It "
"defines which portion of a scene is visible in the rendered image. By default a scene "
"contains one camera. However, a scene can contain more than one camera, but only one of "
"them will be used at a time. So you will only need to add a new camera if you are "
"making cuts between them. See :ref:`Animating Cameras <marker-bind-camera>`."
msgstr ""
"*摄像机* 物体，是Blender为渲染图像所提供的一种工具，用它来指定场景中哪个部分是可见的而用"
"以渲染，默认场景下包含一个摄像机。然而一个场景可以有多个摄像机，但只有其中一个会被使用。"
"如果你在减少场景对象时把他们删了的话，你只需要再添加一个新的“摄像机”即可。请参阅 :ref:`"
"动画相机<marker-bind-camera>`."

