#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:27
msgid ""
"The *active* camera is the camera that is currently being used for rendering and camera "
"view :kbd:`Numpad0`."
msgstr "这个活动的摄像机目前用于渲染和相机视图 :kbd:`Numpad0`。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:30
msgid ""
"Select the camera you would like to make active and press :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad0` (by doing "
"so, you also switch the view to camera view). In order to render, each scene **must** "
"have an active camera."
msgstr ""
"选择您想将其作为新的活动摄像机的摄像机，并按 :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad0` （这样,您也可以将视图切"
"换到摄像机视图）。每个场景 **必须** 有一个活动摄像机用以渲染。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:34
msgid "The active camera can also be set in the *Scene* tab of the *Properties Editor*."
msgstr "活动摄像机也可以通过 *属性编辑器* 中的 *场景* 选项卡设置。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:36
msgid ""
"The camera with the solid triangle on top is the active camera. Limit and mist "
"indicators of cameras are drawn darker if the camera is not the active camera for the "
"current scene."
msgstr ""
"活动摄像机上方的三角形是实心的，当前场景中受限制或者不是活动摄像机的摄像机对象上方的三角"
"形则是线框表示。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:41
msgid ""
"The active camera, as well as the layers, can be specific to a given view, or global "
"(locked) to the whole scene. See :doc:`Local Camera </editors/3dview/properties/"
"panels>`."
msgstr ""
"通过活动摄像机及图层可以是指定的视图，也可以是全局（锁定）到整个场景。请参阅 :doc:"
"`Local Camera </editors/3dview/properties/panels>`."

