#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:61
msgid ""
"While in camera view, you can define a subregion to render by drawing out a rectangle "
"within the camera's frame. Your renders will now be limited to the part of scene "
"visible within the render border. This can be very useful for reducing render times for "
"quick previews on an area of interest."
msgstr ""
"在摄像机视图中，您可以通过在摄像机的框架内绘制一个矩形来定义要渲染的范围。然后渲染将被限"
"制在边界范围内的可见部分。这对缩短预览在感兴趣的区域的渲染时间非常有帮助。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:65
msgid ""
"The border can be disabled by disabling the *Border* option in the *Dimensions* panel "
"in the *Render* tab or by activating the option again."
msgstr ""
"通过在 *渲染* 选项卡的 *规格尺寸* 面板中禁用 *边界范围* 选项或再次激活选项，可以禁用范"
"围。"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/camera/introduction.rst:74
msgid ""
"When Render Border is activated, :doc:`Sampled Motion Blur </render/blender_render/"
"settings/motion_blur>` will become available to view in the 3D View."
msgstr ""
"边界范围被激活时, :doc:`采样运动模糊 </render/blender_render/settings/motion_blur>` 将可"
"在3D视图中查看。"

